<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4612524>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Bathygyge grandis Hansen, 1897, female (CIEGL002801) (A–G): A. Dorsal view. B. Ventral view. C. Left maxilliped, external view. D. Left side of barbula. E. Left oostegite 1, external view. F. Left oostegite 1, internal view. G. Right pereopod 1. Male (CIEGL002801) (H–M): H. Dorsal view. I. Ventral view. J. Antennae and antennule. K. Pereopod 1. L. Pereopod 7. Scale: 2 mm (A, B); 1 mm (D–I); 0.5 mm (C, K–M); 0.25 mm (J)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4612524/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

